item.title: Need help making myself Owner/Admin on a 637
item.dc:creator: @Ozank Ozank
item.description:
@Ozank wrote:

I think you go to your player file in build/data/characters/mainsave (something like this) - change your rights from 0 to 3 (I think 3 is owner, 2 is admin at least so try 2 if 3 doesn’t work)

Hope this helps.
